aretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-in-shooting-attack-near-west-bank-settlement-of-eli/0000018d-f5d1-dd0a-afcf-ffd7af930000</link><description>附近一家餐馆的老板开枪打死了这名恐怖分子，这名恐怖分子是一名前巴勒斯坦警察，此前曾在以色列被监禁过</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 19:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-in-shooting-attack-near-west-bank-settlement-of-eli/0000018d-f5d1-dd0a-afcf-ffd7af930000</guid></item><item><title>30,000 人死亡。饥饿者的踩踏。人质死亡。加沙战争必须结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-29/ty-article/.highlight/30-000-dead-a-stampede-of-the-starving-hostages-dying-the-war-in-gaza-has-to-end/0000018d-f621-d72b-a18d-f7f12cd10000</link><description>今天，每个人都可以添加两个新的理由来结束战争。今天，加沙人被杀的人数达到了30,000人。加沙北部的巴勒斯坦人为救援卡车而打斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 18:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-29/ty-article/.highlight/30-000-dead-a-stampede-of-the-starving-hostages-dying-the-war-in-gaza-has-to-end/0000018d-f621-d72b-a18d-f7f12cd10000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 146 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-146/0000018d-f60b-dd0a-afcf-ffdfcfdf0000</link><description>哈马斯和以色列国防军对加沙中部 110 多名等待粮食援助的巴勒斯坦人死亡的说法相互矛盾 ■ 拜登：周一不太可能达成协议 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：自战争开始以来，已有 30,000 多名加沙人丧生，70,000 多人受伤 ■ 联合国人权高专办酋长：各方都犯下了战争罪行 ■ 战争开始146天后，你需要知道这些</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 18:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-146/0000018d-f60b-dd0a-afcf-ffdfcfdf0000</guid></item><item><title>无法超越“罗”！袋鼠性格诠释赢得“舞蹈你的博士”竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-29/ty-article/cant-outdo-the-roo-interpretation-of-kangaroo-personalities-wins-dance-your-phd-contest/0000018d-f4ec-d401-a3dd-